  fhir:description [ fhir:v "This profile sets minimum expectations for an Organization resource in the context of a patient summary in an Australian context. It is based on the [AU Core Organization](http://hl7.org.au/fhir/core/StructureDefinition/au-core-organization) profile, and applies the additional requirements from [Organization (IPS)](http://hl7.org/fhir/uv/ips/StructureDefinition/Organization-uv-ips)."] ; # 
